= File

`p621.posts.*File*`

== attributes

[cols='1,1,5']
|===
|`_list[int]_`
|`*dimensions*`
|width and height of the file

|`_str_`
|`*extension*`
|file extension

|`_int_`
|`*size*`
|file size in bytes

|`_str_`
|`*md5*`
|preview image of the post

|`_str_`
|`*url*`
|URL of the file (not the page)
|===
